<paragraph id="B26A68C513673148F72C587DFFEBBA0E" pageId="0" pageNumber="62878">
TENERIFE: Arona, Palm-Mar, Paseo Avutarda, wall of manhole, persistent since 2015, 18.12.2018, 
<emphasis id="6B9E88969694FF7255DE72E54DE51975" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="62878">F. Verloove</emphasis>
